      "totalCount": 72450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2158&rangeEnd=2182",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2158&rangeEnd=2182"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_14_1156-1247",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1156-1247",
      "markText": "我之所以会跟这样的女人结婚，是因为她没有什么特别的魅力，同时也找不出什么特别的缺点。在她平凡的性格里，根本看不到令人眼前一亮、善于察言观色和成熟稳重的一面。正因为这样，我才觉得舒坦。",
      "totalCount": 67167,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1156&rangeEnd=1247",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1156&rangeEnd=1247"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_14_1534-1572",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1534-1572",
      "markText": "从一开始，那些用漂亮、聪明、娇艳和富家千金来形容的女子，只会让我感到不自在。",
      "totalCount": 43455,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1534&rangeEnd=1572",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1534&rangeEnd=1572"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_18_1805-1829",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "1805-1829",
      "markText": "大姨子讲电话时掺杂的鼻音，总是能刺激到我的性欲。",
      "totalCount": 38420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1805&rangeEnd=1829",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=1805&rangeEnd=1829"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_14_2206-2250",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "2206-2250",
      "markText": "与其这样，还不如在胸罩里加一张厚实点的胸垫。这样一来，跟朋友见面时，我也好显得有点面子。",
      "totalCount": 34850,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2250",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2206&rangeEnd=2250"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_18_9368-9469",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "9368-9469",
      "markText": "岳父的这份父爱感动得我心头一热，眼眶不自觉地湿润了。大概在座的所有人也都被这一幕感动了。妻子却用手推开了半空中微微颤抖的筷子。 “爸，我不吃肉！”",
      "totalCount": 32827,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9368&rangeEnd=9469",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=9368&rangeEnd=9469"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_14_2424-2486",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "2424-2486",
      "markText": "我没有穿过胸罩，自然无从得知那有多难以忍受。但看到其他女人都没有像她这样讨厌穿胸罩，所以我才会对她的这种过激反应感到很诧异。",
      "totalCount": 32704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2424&rangeEnd=2486",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=2424&rangeEnd=2486"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_14_1853-1894",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1853-1894",
      "markText": "说到兴趣爱好，她似乎只有看书而已，而且看的都是那些我连碰都不想碰的、枯燥无味的书。",
      "totalCount": 31195,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1853&rangeEnd=1894",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1853&rangeEnd=1894"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_31_4856-4931",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "4856-4931",
      "markText": "她安静地吸了一口气，紧盯着路边“熊熊燃烧”的树木，它们就像无数头站立起的野兽，散发着绿光。她的眼神幽暗而执着，像是在等待着回答，不，更像是在表达抗议。",
      "totalCount": 28118,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=4856&rangeEnd=4931",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=4856&rangeEnd=4931"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_19_7570-7645",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "7570-7645",
      "markText": "我扒开妻子紧攥的右手，一只被掐在虎口窒息而死的鸟掉在了长椅上。那是一只掉了很多羽毛的暗绿绣眼鸟，它身上留有捕食者咬噬的牙印，红色的血迹清晰地漫延开来。",
      "totalCount": 26970,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=7570&rangeEnd=7645",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=7570&rangeEnd=7645"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_17_2031-2065",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "2031-2065",
      "markText": "男人们围坐在客厅喝酒、烤肉的时候，女人们则聚在厨房里热热闹闹地聊天。",
      "totalCount": 26824,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2031&rangeEnd=2065",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2031&rangeEnd=2065"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_18_2931-2961",
      "chapterUid": 18,
      "range": "2931-2961",
      "markText": "“你这是闹什么，就算你不吃肉，可你那年轻气盛的老公怎么办？”",
      "totalCount": 26610,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2931&rangeEnd=2961",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=18&rangeStart=2931&rangeEnd=2961"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_24_2379-2424",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "2379-2424",
      "markText": "但眼下他只想为自己辩解，正是因为妻子的忍耐和善意令自己透不过气，所以才会让自己变得更糟糕。",
      "totalCount": 26604,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=2379&rangeEnd=2424",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=2379&rangeEnd=2424"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_14_1313-1376",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "1313-1376",
      "markText": "我那二十五岁之后隆起的小腹，和再怎么努力也长不出肌肉的纤瘦四肢，以及总是令我感到自卑的短小阴茎，这些对她来讲都是无关紧要的事。",
      "totalCount": 26260,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1313&rangeEnd=1376",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=1313&rangeEnd=1376"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_27_7321-7383",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "7321-7383",
      "markText": "身为女儿、姐姐、妻子、母亲和经营店铺的生意人，甚至作为在地铁里与陌生人擦肩而过的行人，她都会竭尽所能地努力扮演好自己的角色。",
      "totalCount": 25585,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=7321&rangeEnd=7383",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=7321&rangeEnd=7383"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "40740496_15_1591-1620",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "1591-1620",
      "markText": "这是结婚五年来，我第一次在没有妻子的照料和送别下出门上班。",
      "totalCount": 25095,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=40740496&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1591&rangeEnd=1620",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/2ff32410726da6902ff40f0?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=1591&rangeEnd=1620"
    },
    {
